<p>Well, a few are original to me (the headscarf woman, the woman with the guitar, the old man) others are based on other versions of Wondertainment on the site (the wild west woman from a plan of Vince's, the Tinkerer, the Wonka + Warden image everyone goes for), then we have both St. Nicholas and Santa, expys of Mabel Pines (and Waddles), Starfire (and Silkie), and r63'd Varrick.</p>
<p>And Weird Al. He's Wondertainment now. This is canon. I have made it so.</p>

